      • is_a

        public boolean is_a(KisaoTerm otherTerm)
        Boolean test for whether this term IS-A subtype of the otherTerm argument. If this.equals(otherTerm), this method returns true.
        So, if otherTerm is the root term (KISAO:0000000), for any subtype, 
            anyterm.is_a(otherTerm) == true;
        Parameters:
        otherTerm - The KisaoTerm under test.
        Returns:
        true if this object IS-A term, false otherwise.
